@startuml
' Scope: student invitation acceptance and tenant binding
' Related: UC-01, FR-INV-01, BR-INV-01, NFR-SEC-01
title 生徒招待・登録 シーケンス図
autonumber

actor "先生" as Teacher
actor "生徒" as Student
participant "createInvite\nServer Action" as Create
participant "acceptInvite\nServer Action" as Accept
participant "NextAuth auth()" as Auth
database "PostgreSQL\nPrisma" as DB

Teacher -> Create : 名前・学年を送信
Create -> Auth : セッションとteacher roleを確認
Auth --> Create : teacherId
Create -> DB : InviteTokenを作成\n[teacherId, expiresAt=7日後]
DB --> Create : token
Create --> Teacher : 招待URL

Student -> Accept : token、メール、パスワードを送信
Accept -> DB : token + usedAt=null + expiresAt>nowを検索
alt 無効、期限切れ、使用済み
  DB --> Accept : not found
  Accept --> Student : 招待を受理しない
else 有効
  DB --> Accept : InviteToken(teacherId)
  Accept -> DB : transaction開始
  Accept -> DB : User(role=student)を作成
  Accept -> DB : Student(userId, teacherId)を作成
  Accept -> DB : InviteToken.usedAtを更新
  Accept -> DB : transaction commit
  Accept --> Student : /dashboardへ遷移
end

note over Accept,DB
  teacherIdはクライアント入力ではなく、
  検証済みInviteTokenから引き継ぐ。
end note
@enduml

